<ul>
<li><strong>AI Mode shows 68% fewer businesses</strong> than traditional local packs, making every optimization decision more consequential</li>
<li><strong>The AI Signal Mapping Framework</strong> connects each GBP field to the specific AI signal it feeds, eliminating guesswork</li>
